From e188fd18f9c798d62c631c0f7827326db8dbbe36 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
Date: Fri, 20 Feb 2026 17:34:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 16/26] test: boot: add imagemap unit tests

Add a test suite exercising the imagemap translation-table core:

 - map, lookup, and map_to operations
 - cleanup releases all tracked allocations
 - region growth via alist (dynamic region list)
 - edge cases: zero-length reads, overlapping regions

The tests use a trivial RAM-backed read callback, so they run on
sandbox without any real storage device.

Registered under ut_boot_imagemap in cmd_ut.c and built when
CONFIG_IMAGEMAP is enabled in the sandbox test configuration.

Signed-off-by: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
---
Changes since RFC:
  - Renamed image_loader to imagemap
  - Switched from fixed MAX_REGIONS array to dynamic alist (Tom)
  - Concise ut_assert*() style (Simon)
  - Test declarations immediately follow function body (Simon)
